name: breeze.labs.js
description:
Breeze Labs is a collection of JavaScript libraries that
  assist development of Breeze-based applications.
  They are not part of breeze core. They are often experimental.
  We (IdeaBlade) offer them to you "as is" with no
  promise of support and they have a higher risk of breaking changes.
  Please visit the Breeze Labs github for details.
